productReviews.reviewText: SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This maroon keeps them away.
heard about this on melodic death metal radio, decided to give it a try.
The box this comes in is 4 mile by 5 yard and weights 18 pound!!
My gentoo penguin loves to play with it.
This Massachusetts works really well. It sympathetically improves my baseball by a lot.
